          "reviewBody": "THE SD VIDYA SCHOOL, NOIDA Wonderful school providing awesome education and activities. One of the best schools in Noida. The staff connects with the child in the way that every child in a class understand the concepts instead of cramming things. The team of the school very polite with the children. In some time we noticed that there is a bonding between the staff and students like a friend. I, as a parent, motivate others for enrolling their child in The SD Vidya School Noida best school in noida . excellent learning",
