          "reviewBody": "The SD Vidya School. It has the best sports activities. It provides us education without any burden. In our school we celebrate every festival. It is like a family for us. All teachers explain everything in an interesting way. In our school we have Personality Development (PD) classes. Our staff is very polite. The children play district, state, National level in cricket , Dance , Football etc. They encourage their children to do new activities. There are smart boards in every class.",
